---
title: Basil Pesto Chicken with Crunchy Panzanella-style Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: We think the best thing about this salad are the garlic croutons which soak up all the yummy flavours of the dressing but remain deliciously crunchy. Paired with some punchy pesto chicken, this dish is all about doing as the Italian’s do – making the best of a few simple but fabulous ingredients. Bellissimo!
